                        <span class="blogHeadline">Nikki contest results on Monday</span>
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <small>Saturday, July 23rd, 2011</small>

                <div>
                    <div class="en"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-full wp-image-1047 alignnone" title="Nikki and the Robots Time" src="http://joyridelabs.de/blog//wp-content/uploads/2011/07/time.png" alt="Nikki and the Robots Time" width="22" height="22" /></p>
